summary: Only One More Online Smash Tournament Before The PAX East Finals
title: Only One More Online Smash Tournament Before The PAX East Finals
body:
Only One More Online Smash Tournament Before The PAX East Finals

This weekend, players from four regions across North America are competing in the third and final wave of online finals for the Super Smash Bros. Ultimate North America Open 2019 tournament. You can watch it live by visiting either https://www.twitch.tv/Nintendo or https://www.youtube.com/Nintendo. 

Livestreaming starts at approximately 9 a.m. PT on Saturday, March 16, for all…
